The Men Magazine - Jan Feb 2014

327 Pages | True PDF | English | 84 MB 


The Men International is the first global lifestyle magazine conceived with the idea of truly informing and uniting people worldwide. Our entire planet today is an exciting melting pot of different cultures and histories who, still, share common goals, dreams and beliefs, more connected than ever. Thanks to the internet, education and the media, local becomes global and borders are erased. This is where The Men comes in, as we will tell you how to make money or seduce a beautiful woman, where to eat, what to wear and who to watch.
